Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 186 of the Penal Code\NA person who habitually gambles or bets shall be punished by hard labor for not more than 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi Hideyuki, the world's foremost busting out machine. From Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oda Shintarou, an ippatsu chad ignorant of theory. From Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokugawa Yasubee, a nyagger with zero understanding of mahjong theory. From Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi Kouichi, an experienced player who plays an extremely logical mahjong. From Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayami Akina. Supposedly Toyotomi's girlfriend and the possessor of astounding good luck. From Chiba prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uooohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pools in midwinter are really the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a feast for the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uooohhh! Zekkoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Booba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting​!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,POOLSIDE ZUGOOMERS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina's akinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uoohhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Awooga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea cucumbers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Two huge red sea cucumbers stuck together!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Retard, this isn't the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get close to it! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tfu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a red sea cucumber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude! Can't even get left alone and swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go back to my room and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy, what was the deal with his way of swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been Undersea Humanoid Ragon!\N(TN: big-lipped fishman from the {\i1}Ultraman{\i0} series)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wutcha doin' there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You all went without me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault you were lazin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you came here too, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'd like to have something cold to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Toyotomi! Don't just stand around and buy us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! You just sit down with us, Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Four colas, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wutcha doin'?! Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only enough for four ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I told ya, ya dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about mine ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fuckin' with me! Pay for your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My own ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But ... I don't have any money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, he started to cry just from a cola. Kek, what a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then ya shouldn't have come here with us anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina, if you spoil him he'll get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, buy yourself something nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic guy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"DELICIOUS YAKITORI"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Five colas, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Douzo, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigatoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher Ozawa Takeshobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozawa Takeshobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Famed as the user of the unbeatable rage harvesting technique ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he is an invulnerable mahjonger who has returned from death many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Master ... you were alive after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What should you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, it's been a long time, you old prankster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have mistaken me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I am certainly no "Ozawa" you speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then who are you?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your cola, so get the bloody hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I politely ask you to not come in the vicinity of this stand again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, I can't let you pull mischief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a good boy and sit over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut? I'm busy right now! No time to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Such a good hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "help" is uncalled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Cutting that one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd cut this one instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then cutting this would guarantee a yaku ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did like I told you, you'd be in 14m tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?! Riichi?! That's totally the wrong move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ippatsu tsumo! Riichi instant tsumo tanyao sanshoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Ura ura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,N-never mind ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit! I have no safe tiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, point read!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina's wait is definitely 36m!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A 36m wait, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,36m!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut 3m!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww ... pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no safe tiles at all, but luckily Toyotomi's reads are guaranteed to be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as good as genbutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop ruining the game, ToyotomI!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I ... didn't want to ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop ruining it! It's your bedtime already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuyashii ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A voucher for a free night's lodging and dinner at this hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We should give it back to them ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Toyotomi, it's mahjong time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sit out, you guys have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go! Start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, idiot. I'll beat him and the dinner voucher's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That faggot Toyotomi brought something nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,After you all go back to your rooms, it'll be just me and Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is another great haipai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I can hear the sound of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew it! Ryuuiisou tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,WRYYY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With this wait, 7s is just 5200!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call 3s and wait on 3s tanki, it'll come out easily with the 4s pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's gooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He called? Ron eet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyao sanshoku iipeikou dora dora! 18000!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut? He got shadowrealmed before I got a chance to ron him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. The dinner voucher will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The luxury lodging and dinner voucher Toyotomi found!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this mysterious character who seemed to be its owner ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The supposedly late Ozawa Takeshobo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, what conclusion is waiting for Toyotomi and Akina?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The turbulent second act will begin in about 80 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Expect the point of view of all concerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,East 1, North seat, 9th turn, 25000 points\NDora 4p, tsumo 8p
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshoku is ... le GOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's my comeback hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Comeback?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How are ya gonna come back from –60k?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Comeback" is not a word to be used lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone should still be allowed to have hopes and dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he deserves a human rights tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, whether you're a frog, bug, or poor as a church rat, you deserve to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We're all frens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fucking with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,RETURN OF THE OLD MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Check 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut 2s for 1p3s shanpon! Cut 3s for 14s ryanmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This one and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ippatsu tsumo and get ura 3, it's baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, with just one hand ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be at –44k!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cut 3s I would have ippatsu tsumo'd!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Out-squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, I got to tenpai ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I finish first if I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No other words after "riichi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What, riichi nomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Retard! I have to look at the ura first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Ura 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ura! Ura! Told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's 2600 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,3200! 3200! I get extra points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the hand, adeptchad! If I get screwed out of my points every hand, that's no business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 50 fu! 50!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With 2600 or 3200, your end score is still -107!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoko doko ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Mangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, Toyotomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-there was something weird outside the window ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything here or there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But there definitely was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were daydreaming, weren't ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So weird ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, such an annoying false alarm kind of guy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck are {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait ... I've seen him before somewhere ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! It's Ozawa Takeshobo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct! Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I'm so happy to see you again ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My disciple ...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That ugly old man from the stand was you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you youngsters were playing mah-jongg?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Would you like to play too, Master? Please show your true power to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's a good feeling to touch the tiles again ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Humu humu? I see, I see ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to cut this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's talking to himself ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like me can hear the voice of the tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice of the tiles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. The tiles are alive and have a heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A true adept can rise above common sense and flow like water, discaring what the tiles tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I'll try to listen to the tiles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you berievu in za Gahdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're trying to be funny, I'm calling riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, these youngsters are always calling riichi too early ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Which one ... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wait is 36p!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I hit the bullseye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know my wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The discards have a voice of their own ... and they told me 36p is your wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ippatsu! Riichi ippatsu tanyao iipeikou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man ... you will die a good death ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Pinfu ittsuu, 5200! [sic]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Honitsu ton, mangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Riichi chanta sanshoku dora dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any pity for an old man like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen young people like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, like this Master is guaranteed to come in last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for my ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi to confirm 3rd place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me, Toyotomi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was secretly waiting for you to make this mistake all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Apoplexy riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to know? You want to know ... its meaning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? Apoplexy suddenly attacks you one day and then ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you're certain to fall over dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's high calorie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apoplexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told you to pay attention to your calorie intake ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm tenpai again ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That wait is ... look, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see ... it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ippatsu tsumo Alzheimer tanki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiten tanki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you tsumo that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb boomer ... I'll show him the power of our generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Subarachnoid hemorrhage riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Social security chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Super express retirement home return!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu honitsu shousangen, baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory for the young!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bedridden old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop foolin' around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that death has come calling for me ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to eat a hotel dinner before ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! We have a ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's for me and Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My luxury lodging and dinner voucher for five people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going to steal it, weren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the food's tasty and the show's great too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good! Yeah, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Arigatoh for treating us, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as people don't do bad deeds, we're all friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, tonight's special guest, the abominable snowman ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Lucklet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm innocent!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The outcry of Toyotomi's heart was drowned out by the flames of the burning limbo and the cheers of the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi, let me offer these lines to you:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks might be / compared to a storm\Nbut the only thing I say goodbye to / is life.
